text: Johann König (born 21 September 1932) is an Austrian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Bregenz Category:Sportspeople from Vorarlberg
